{"tid":1631764,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔理分唔分化，全部手足都要達成一個共識","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:43.000Z","uid":204975,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"adbe0f4d681a9269b3c3307ad1012c56e407808e","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:15:36.000Z","msg":"文宣的確做得唔足<br />\n國際戰線的確非常緊急<br />\n希望各位可以正視呢啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">問題</span></span><br />\n達成一個共識係要做好文宣，做好[black]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑裝修！</span>[/black]<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">紅裝飾！</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃幫襯！</span></span><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">藍罷買！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不分化啊各位，文宣係首要目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd789e51b6db57f5e2169548957569fa8e9d4e6","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:16:00.000Z","msg":"我知好多人好攰"},{"pid":"c96f81f9d1afb96a1abd63dbeb239b50693827ea","tid":1631764,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:16:06.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"1c1fe70a360c355a331f19f33704873beabfb5e2","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:16:18.000Z","msg":"直路啦各位"},{"pid":"69f58072ae906a7001e4ab1e6927a23ecb1fbcfb","tid":1631764,"uid":175806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:16:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">7號晚係關鍵！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">要令黨鐵全線第二日停駛</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">港豬們好耐未三罷啦</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n香港人．<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反抗</span></span><br />\n香港人．三罷</span>"},{"pid":"d0537a70d2783de94334289b01f4031ab438a363","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:16:52.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"f4a8631d24a2cdd3ec60e3dc165e856a43c2a227","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:17:38.000Z","msg":"唔可以輸"},{"pid":"b79ae634fa7a2d85faf64c03e75b1319ef2db658","tid":1631764,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:17:46.000Z","msg":"真係要達成共識先做到文宣，唔係文宣做左，但又打爆d唔係本身範圍架店，文宣好難做"},{"pid":"0ec3ee2fadf6b4af6152eb5fc2dcee98f7edc507","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b79ae634fa7a2d85faf64c03e75b1319ef2db658","tid":1631764,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:17:46.000Z","msg":"真係要達成共識先做到文宣，唔係文宣做左，但又打爆d唔係本身範圍架店，文宣好難做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:21:53.000Z","msg":"冇心嘅"},{"pid":"6f9663c1385e87baa8b412e852caa23383f6041c","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:23:24.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"193f809932cfd789a97f8990af69f34c296837f4","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:24:07.000Z","msg":"文宣文宣文宣"},{"pid":"9b5b71a5c6cb803855c8f3a9ef7ee78dc4580c02","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:26:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"03535d28a38035a48cdb5123654616dd21cc2e42","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:28:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d1fee2690276cb7a77435f084736dc726b5dc021","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"71718c83297124519505118033249d77978504d7","tid":1631764,"uid":175091,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:04.000Z","msg":"對準十八區既政權標誌 做好文宣好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n14年係因為大台輸<br />\n19年我地要自省進化 人不犯我我不犯人<br />\n唔好因爲自己輸 不分化<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aou2kEE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAou2kEE.png&h=cd86d455&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c80589cd51b5bac8fa38b5b9a2bc01708f9c20f3","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:28.000Z","msg":"文宣"},{"pid":"da5778ed3c0b188cf1be55b7e7dd22f7e13b9265","tid":1631764,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adbe0f4d681a9269b3c3307ad1012c56e407808e","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:15:36.000Z","msg":"文宣的確做得唔足<br />\n國際戰線的確非常緊急<br />\n希望各位可以正視呢啲<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">問題</span></span><br />\n達成一個共識係要做好文宣，做好[black]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑裝修！</span>[/black]<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">紅裝飾！</span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃幫襯！</span></span><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">藍罷買！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不分化啊各位，文宣係首要目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:38.000Z","msg":"國際輿論開始轉風向：<br />\n<br />\nBBC:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49949548\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49949548&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL7XdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=6ba053ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49949548&h=20132a5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49949548</a><br />\nAnti-government marches in Hong Kong have ended in rioting, with attacks on government offices, a metro station and businesses with ties to mainland China.<br />\n<br />\nCNN:<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL7XdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=db5a5519\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&h=53844d7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html</a><br />\nViolent protests which began Friday stretched into the early hours of Saturday, beyond the midnight deadline when the new anti-mask regulations began. They spread out across the city and soon devolved into violent clashes, with protesters throwing petrol bombs and police responding with pepper spray and tear gas.<br />\n<br />\nUN rights chief :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F10%2F06%2Fun-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence%2F&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL7XdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=825ffcca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence/</a><br />\nUN human rights chief Michelle Bachelet said Saturday she was &ldquo;troubled&rdquo; by Hong Kong&rsquo;s increasingly violent pro-democracy protests<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fm6HkAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFm6HkAU.jpg&h=cfadcc90&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DNQQuuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDNQQuuf.jpg&h=e8fe24d4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dkz2kAV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdkz2kAV.jpg&h=e42958dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wt3FRHB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWt3FRHB.jpg&h=836cc635&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n開始無人話警察武力不對等，國際開始支持港府。再係咁落去，美國人權及民主法案好可能被否決<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以做多D外國文宣 (Twitter), 唔好覺得有班人會做, 人人都要文宣!!"},{"pid":"bbdf4d9aafb9d1cc79f678aae3e61e32037123c6","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:47.000Z","msg":"Airdrops 連儂牆"},{"pid":"667f17df33e5099679b87ba15373689d76db13a2","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:04.000Z","msg":"辛苦文宣組"},{"pid":"b73942b7345616a50427f416def91b671204aa07","tid":1631764,"uid":56277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:39.000Z","msg":"唔好再斟酌去拗對與錯，大家需要係善意嘅指正而唔係指責 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fdf23db2821cb73d6555322d5c4715cc3c9a077","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:32:53.000Z","msg":"文宣"},{"pid":"0b05fda05b160f83bb91dfe9173a5fcc6d0e37f7","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:35:34.000Z","msg":"文宣啊"},{"pid":"924d35ccb25b4eba08fb3fbfefa8665e2c8245f2","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:36:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c61c9e991b967747c703a4391c7f83a21ba833a5","tid":1631764,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:36:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6c7180cc072a2d196adf87696df836a21d4ca3a","tid":1631764,"uid":204975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}